Turia Pitt suffered horrific burns to 65 per cent of her body when she competed in an ultra-marathon in Kimberley in September 2011 .
The 27-year-old said just the smell from a barbecue brought back the traumatic moment she was trapped for four hours .
She ran her first marathon last month and clocked a faster time than before .
Ms Pitt is currently training ahead of the 10-day fund raising trek along the Inca Trail in Peru .